    "body": "It will probably take a while for me to chew through the fine details of this PR (especially since I want to prioritize finishing my mod support PRs and then wrestling the PR queue into something managable), but my initial reactions based on the PR description are:\r\n\r\n* I like where you're going with this, and it will be a really powerful feature if we do it right.\r\n* Before we go any further down the rabbit hole we *really* need to think about how to and then implement auto-generated documentation for the ConditionProperties, etc, that each trait exposes.  Not necessarily in this PR, but certainly no later than the next one."
